{"tid":197582,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【千年大計】北京首都變病都 來自毛澤東一個決定","createTime":"2017-04-12T03:19:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-12T06:08:52.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ae7595b3236624898e68d8103b232012de564cc5","tid":197582,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T03:19:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170411/large/1491908647_5c95.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170411%2Flarge%2F1491908647_5c95.jpg&h=ad26d67e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一千年前的中國為宋朝，當時的北京地區屬於遼國，「北京」其實並不存在。北京首次成為全國首都是在金朝，距今只有約900年。中國官方此次以「千年大計」形容雄安新區，對全國造成震撼，意味將是一個非常長期的工程，亦顯示正視北京目前大都市病的決心。<br />\n<br />\n北京所處的華北平原嚴重缺水，其實並不適宜作為首都。但在1949年，毛澤東出於避開南方國民黨遺留官僚資本的政治考慮，定都北京。當時知名建築師梁思成提出在北京城外成立行政中心，保留市區內古建築，但毛澤東聽取蘇聯專家的建議，決定把北京建設成「屬於工人階級的生產性城市」，建造大批工廠和企業，發展成經濟中心，並大肆拆除市內文物建築。<br />\n時至今日，北京已成為全國行政中心，以及大部分央企，以及金融機構總部的所在地，並雲集全國約三分之一的大學，人口達到約2,200萬人，資源不堪負荷。市內交通嚴重堵塞，霧霾舉世知名。中央更需投資過千億「南水北調」工程，才能解決用水問題。<br />\n除環境問題外，北京的樓價問題亦為外界詬病。目前北京樓價均價為每平方米約6萬元人民幣，10年間漲7倍，已經超出居民購買力，亦令大量在北京畢業的大學生無法落戶，造成人才流失。為免重蹈覆轍，當局在宣佈成立雄安新區，第一時間在當地嚴打炒樓，凍結所有房產買賣，並在周邊10個城市實施限購。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20170412/56551623\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20170412%2F56551623&d=74s%2FNZguDZpTF4W18ni10E%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=b62000f9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20170412%2F56551623&h=b2043c62\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20170412/56551623</a>"},{"pid":"f8a9a7f395d6a3ccbe5714c3764de4de8c530258","tid":197582,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T03:26:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5a7d005404ca0a33e8966a0dc1d4e809664476a","tid":197582,"uid":3794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T03:27:46.000Z","msg":"依家啲人先開始後悔冇聽梁思成講 聽埋哂啲垃圾蛾佬講 梁思成堂堂民國一大建築師都唔撚聽 梁思成九泉之下見到依家都咁彈返起身"},{"pid":"7d3196bf70dbd34a5a809797e1650731e331c54d","tid":197582,"uid":39365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T03:44:27.000Z","msg":"叫北京魔都其實無錯, D妖魔鬼怪係晒度"},{"pid":"bcb2a51b92064de735d1d8cad244796b17df9798","tid":197582,"uid":37808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T03:46:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>叫北京魔都其實無錯, D妖魔鬼怪係晒度</blockquote><br />\n魔都唔係上海咩"},{"pid":"0c7625d484db08339415414c75459add65c38176","tid":197582,"uid":61271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T03:51:29.000Z","msg":"其實明清都係以北京為首都，又有無出過問題?"},{"pid":"bc7d952051b4987a71946d82850a0d4b9eb01067","tid":197582,"uid":54305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T03:51:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>依家啲人先開始後悔冇聽梁思成講 聽埋哂啲垃圾蛾佬講 梁思成堂堂民國一大建築師都唔撚聽 梁思成九泉之下見到依家都咁彈返起身</blockquote><br />\n俄佬唔垃圾，只係佢整個氹比毛魔踩啫。<br />\n而毛魔又真係咁on9踩落去。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c48c074c3d6fa996f1958e7f8e4424e0331c257d","tid":197582,"uid":29804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T03:53:26.000Z","msg":"停左南水北調 會點"},{"pid":"098503941238130a16b3f7871a9484bfbaf586a2","tid":197582,"uid":57607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T03:56:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實明清都係以北京為首都，又有無出過問題?</blockquote><br />\n個陣冇汽車冇高速公路冇10層樓以上建築<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4f1aac243c330a30726f56cdadc92fa133ec342","tid":197582,"uid":24944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T04:02:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>叫北京魔都其實無錯, D妖魔鬼怪係晒度</blockquote><br />\n魔都唔係上海咩</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"223a5ef288b5f2f9358da02f89da90393baec3ea","tid":197582,"uid":6532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T04:06:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>叫北京魔都其實無錯, D妖魔鬼怪係晒度</blockquote><br />\n魔都唔係上海咩</blockquote><br />\nYes, 北京係帝都"},{"pid":"9e0a24a9780b90dae7d466abc9d2f9e292341642","tid":197582,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T04:10:16.000Z","msg":"幾十年前點估計到今日發展到咁"},{"pid":"11f29c37cdac66cedbad40c2c333ef8e17f57da8","tid":197582,"uid":2290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T04:17:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>叫北京魔都其實無錯, D妖魔鬼怪係晒度</blockquote><br />\n魔都唔係上海咩</blockquote><br />\nYes, 北京係帝都</blockquote><br />\n我最記得東莞係性都<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 雖然依家係廢都"},{"pid":"4049cb6739332753e3a276cbf554f4843cb1ac70","tid":197582,"uid":66026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T04:20:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實明清都係以北京為首都，又有無出過問題?</blockquote><br />\n個陣冇汽車冇高速公路冇10層樓以上建築<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n明同清都有做人口控制，同埋冇今日北京咁多經濟上嘅問題，同埋南水北調呢個term都係近年先有"},{"pid":"28850baacb1054da5bc1509334fee95af50e8f01","tid":197582,"uid":64858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T05:01:01.000Z","msg":"屌你連毛魔都捉緊棋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21e1921a292915cf3ca24ce415990c69cec569e2","tid":197582,"uid":45684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T05:04:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾十年前點估計到今日發展到咁</blockquote><br />\n城巿規劃就係睇幾十年甚至幾百年嘅發展"},{"pid":"66771455174fd5c99e779f791e9661ea0d44b323","tid":197582,"uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T05:09:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你連毛魔都捉緊棋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n死左都仲捉到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"808c0c94db697482e51b3a0330377398169f0880","tid":197582,"uid":56453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T05:14:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屌你連毛魔都捉緊棋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n死左都仲捉到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有無睇棋靈王？"},{"pid":"c8036c1d982cb42ac8394387dff59f255e5b4de3","tid":197582,"uid":57607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T05:16:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實明清都係以北京為首都，又有無出過問題?</blockquote><br />\n個陣冇汽車冇高速公路冇10層樓以上建築<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n明同清都有做人口控制，同埋冇今日北京咁多經濟上嘅問題，同埋南水北調呢個term都係近年先有</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n哩個term都係毛澤東講<br />\n只係近二十年開始搞啲全國大工程"},{"pid":"912d8a40bbcc59a6c5b09aa39f59826f57a34d9b","tid":197582,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T06:08:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>幾十年前點估計到今日發展到咁</blockquote><br />\n城巿規劃就係睇幾十年甚至幾百年嘅發展</blockquote><br />\n問題毛主席除左中國歷史同中國文學，係咩都唔識。<br />\n<br />\n當時考慮的嘢亦冇所謂城市規劃概念，因為新中國建立後同好多封建王朝一樣，都有大把內憂外患跟。整個首都的定立及設計，都以政治及軍事出發，並非人民的宜居。"},{"pid":"8ee47abc3d3ca69ff36325de33029f54d24d6d4e","tid":197582,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T06:08:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你連毛魔都捉緊棋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n今日共產黨好多規矩都係沿用老毛遺留的一套。"}]}